Title: Using Corpora to Develop Limited-Domain Speech Translation Systems  
Author: Manny Rayner Pierrette Bouillon ISSCO David Carter 
Address: Suite 23, Millers Yard Cambridge CB2 1RQ United Kingdom  1227 Geneva, Switzerland  Suite 23, Millers Yard Cambridge CB2 1RQ United Kingdom  
